Introduction

Lee Hwanhee is a South Korean singer. He made his official debut on September 10, 2015, as the main vocalist of UP10TION under TOP Media. In 2017, he appeared on the show Masked Singer.

He is best known for participating in the reality survival shows Boys Planet, and Build Up : Vocal Boy Group Survivor.

On June 26, 2023 he took to Instagram to announce he will now be part of PA Entertainment.
